Interface DeltaConfig

All Superinterfaces:
BaseConfiguration, Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
DeltaConfigImpl
public interface DeltaConfig
extends BaseConfiguration

A Delta Configuration can be used by a Connector in Iterator mode.
